eu.shooktea.vmsm.module

Class VMModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.shooktea.vmsm.module.VMModule
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Magento, MySQL, SSH

    public abstract class VMModule
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class representing single module. Module in VMSM is an additional set of tools that can be connected with virtual machine. Every virtual machine can have different set of modules with different configuration. VMType describes which modules can work with given type of virtual machine.

    Because of the way modules work in VMSM, it's constructor should never be called anywhere except in declaration of modules in VMModule class, where new modules are created. Modules there should be effectively singletons.
